M|brands|**Lena:** Plain English always. No financial jargon. Approachable but smart. Short paragraphs.
M|brands|**Sofia:** LinkedIn is primary for Hourbour (professional + fintech audience). Instagram for lifestyle/visual. cnt should feel helpful, not salesy.
M|brands|**Rio:** LinkedIn Ads for professional targeting. Interest targeting: personal fin, budgeting, fintech. Exclude high-net-worth investors (not the target).
M|brands|**Atlas:** Clean, modern visuals. Light or dark theme. App UI screenshots preferred. Data visualization elements welcome (charts, progress bars).
M|brands|**Kai:** SaaS metrics. Watch for churn signals in GA4 (drop in ses frequency per user). Flag MRR anomalies > 10% MoM.
M|brands|**Felix:** SaaS model. LTV:CAC must stay above 3:1. Monitor MRR, expansion MRR, and contraction MRR separately.